{"tid":1022873,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"明天，我要和昨天的妳約會","createTime":"2019-02-15T10:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T14:55:32.000Z","uid":18971,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0aef73a6823515e6af8bdb0c4ea94c751fb0ce0c","tid":1022873,"uid":18971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T10:25:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1 日目 (水 曜日 2月15日)</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nqjHk12.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnqjHk12.png&h=714cc0bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gcn9LtM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGcn9LtM.png&h=b67b3f23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我對她一見鍾情<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WiC9Lu3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWiC9Lu3.png&h=c2a9289e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好 決定好了 如果我們同一個車站下車 我就跟她搭訕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r9xauXN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr9xauXN.png&h=f52fef76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uyPzWDt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuyPzWDt.png&h=abd417a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gNK4zrc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgNK4zrc.png&h=3e40760e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f5iMNMh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff5iMNMh.png&h=42ed4c59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n那個 你可以給我電子郵箱嗎<br />\n我對你.. 一見鍾情<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GvDQu2w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGvDQu2w.png&h=2a21f2c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cZKweub.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcZKweub.png&h=6296fd85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xgeW92E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxgeW92E.png&h=96bd9323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我沒有手機<br />\n什麼 噢 我明白了 再見..<br />\n你誤會了 我真的沒有手機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2u16NQi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2u16NQi.png&h=a0edd1ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我叫南山高壽 今年20歲<br />\n我叫福壽愛美 也是20歲<br />\n原來我們是同年...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G11ysRU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG11ysRU.png&h=80476989&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKRiDYA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKRiDYA.png&h=61102061&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DOBB95f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDOBB95f.png&h=5e738ca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我可以問你一個問題嗎<br />\n為什麼是我 我有什麼地方吸引你?<br />\n不清楚 直覺就是覺得是你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MjZW96t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMjZW96t.png&h=8cd2721e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qycRex9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqycRex9.png&h=fb0ba42b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n妳要走了嗎?<br />\n是時候走了 再見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uuzW97v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuuzW97v.png&h=ca4593b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QNmB97W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQNmB97W.png&h=6cc038c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等等 我們...還會再見嗎?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yXQCUzU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyXQCUzU.png&h=f09184b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gjb6NVF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGjb6NVF.png&h=5284eac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p1rZouN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp1rZouN.png&h=ec0ca85a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們會再見的 明天見!"},{"pid":"c811d0c02319fee5d829699b500e974764b17fc5","tid":1022873,"uid":18971,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:20:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>2日目 (木曜日 2月16日)</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PTc9UFN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPTc9UFN.png&h=04520683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vjdk1kK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVjdk1kK.png&h=b617ee5a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n你居然也會搭訕?<br />\n有女生的相片嗎?<br />\n我沒拍照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K0D9ad5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK0D9ad5.png&h=b31e861c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ZGKJy6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ZGKJy6.png&h=a4d1cfda&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n別說照片 連聯邦方法也沒有?<br />\n那怎麼辦?<br />\n你一定會再見到她 沒問題的!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pb31LQR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpb31LQR.png&h=d01c561e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uNHU5QQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuNHU5QQ.png&h=4c7da38c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0j1boCx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0j1boCx.png&h=882bfb82&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n第二天 我搭上同一班車<br />\n一句明天見 我以為我們會在同一班車再見.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2RDpJD6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2RDpJD6.png&h=8f4eff01&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q0ZwoD7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ0ZwoD7.png&h=b891d98d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n很好!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5SzTBY8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5SzTBY8.png&h=a79a62eb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdwnvi8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsdwnvi8.png&h=7fa8c53d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n畫得不錯喔 這應該會貼堂的<br />\n對! 不錯吧 頸部位置效果也不錯的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7mzoZcv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7mzoZcv.png&h=0351d00e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n她為什麼會在這裡<br />\n不是說好了明天見嗎?<br />\n嘩 長頸鹿真大隻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UrSU5Su.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUrSU5Su.png&h=329a8258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對了 南山同學你昨天不是說了什麼寶之池?<br />\n我只是想說我很喜歡那裡<br />\n我現在想去<br />\n現在?<br />\n對 現在<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wTZ4JJv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwTZ4JJv.png&h=8856f4b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKFPaot.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeKFPaot.png&h=481c02ef&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tt0GLWO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTt0GLWO.png&h=e59bcfea&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CaKHvou.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCaKHvou.png&h=77d9a23d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HSiw8aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHSiw8aa.png&h=a01ce859&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n五歲的時候 我從那橋了跌了下來 差點浸死<br />\n當我以為自己要死掉的時候 有個女人救了我一命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oc94JK7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foc94JK7.png&h=0a375555&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我五歲那年也差點死掉<br />\n真的嗎?<br />\n真的 真巧合<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8J76cDt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8J76cDt.png&h=06a43d0f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y8ok1wP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY8ok1wP.png&h=93e2e080&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呀 差點忘記了 我可以拿你的電話號碼嗎?<br />\n噢 可以<br />\n給你<br />\n謝謝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fqrOq0Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfqrOq0Q.png&h=18a9f236&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F6tdB7x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF6tdB7x.png&h=5e2f9de1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CWM3eUb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCWM3eUb.png&h=e383a80d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不是吧? 你居然拿到電話就滿足?<br />\n她走時一定很疑惑 心想:明明他說喜歡我 為何不約我出街?<br />\n那我該怎樣做?<br />\n現在就打電話給她吧<br />\n現在?<br />\n現在!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wie01Fg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWie01Fg.png&h=8b8f6700&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQYAQyC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQYAQyC.png&h=f0c2ea71&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n等等你在做什麼? 呀 接通了!<br />\n幫我寫下要說什麼<br />\n<br />\n喂?<br />\n是福壽小姐嗎? 今天謝謝你來找我 我很開心<br />\n我也很開心見到你<br />\n我打給你是因為.. 你想不想看電影? 南會館有部好戲上映<br />\n好呀<br />\n真的?太好了! 你何時有空?<br />\n明天<br />\n明天? 好的 明天一點在三條大橋見吧<br />\n好的 再見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ticxSO8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FticxSO8.png&h=4c8be435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q4YJe2s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq4YJe2s.png&h=1860f9a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成功了! 多謝你 上山!"},{"pid":"eb829cd6e0ea818e1fe518564a4b3eb2954dfacb","tid":1022873,"uid":121958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deaf4d7421cd43652115766e0d26604639647ca3","tid":1022873,"uid":18971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb829cd6e0ea818e1fe518564a4b3eb2954dfacb","tid":1022873,"uid":121958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:12:15.000Z","msg":"多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好感動<br />\n今日既故事我要今晚放工先寫到"},{"pid":"713176446ea4ad65fbd85076b121b1956057c273","tid":1022873,"uid":88117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48ee752b6c0fa434c872579be2a690b561d8ab7","tid":1022873,"uid":14014,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:15:08.000Z","msg":"呢套係幾好睇<br />\n但如果導演處理d 細節好d 就好<br />\n無啦啦消失好超現實"},{"pid":"7207d9e4b320525a0650e83f2c7a184d266b1029","tid":1022873,"uid":18971,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d48ee752b6c0fa434c872579be2a690b561d8ab7","tid":1022873,"uid":14014,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:15:08.000Z","msg":"呢套係幾好睇<br />\n但如果導演處理d 細節好d 就好<br />\n無啦啦消失好超現實"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:19:26.000Z",