me":"2019-02-17T12:19:26.000Z","msg":"個故事就係超現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T13:33:29.000Z","msg":"當然時空穿越一定會超現實<br />\n但如果導演處理好呢d 細節就會令觀眾代入感大d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順帶一提男主d 戲好左<br />\n以前睇佢真係秒速出戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b144e2ef4ae8437d9fc3ca666a4cb39778199d1f","tid":1022873,"uid":18971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a62e827c152259c9beddf8a3caf3a0973b8ad46","tid":1022873,"uid":14014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7207d9e4b320525a0650e83f2c7a184d266b1029","tid":1022873,"uid":18971,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d48ee752b6c0fa434c872579be2a690b561d8ab7","tid":1022873,"uid":14014,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:15:08.000Z","msg":"呢套係幾好睇<br />\n但如果導演處理d 細節好d 就好<br />\n無啦啦消失好超現實"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:19:26.000Z","msg":"個故事就係超現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T13:33:29.000Z","msg":"當然時空穿越一定會超現實<br />\n但如果導演處理好呢d 細節就會令觀眾代入感大d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順帶一提男主d 戲好左<br />\n以前睇佢真係秒速出戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T13:51:24.000Z","msg":"但好多人都覺得佢d戲仲好屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得都仲ok ge<br />\n但小松菜奈演技真係好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fbabd93315517495e48c16313798d7f87ce2813","tid":1022873,"uid":18971,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gWSVerb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgWSVerb.png&h=1571b43c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qA2BJjw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqA2BJjw.png&h=af2eaab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上山給了我一點約會小貼士<br />\n就是見面前早點到附近探路<br />\n避免因迷路而緊張變得不可靠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/atvr5xS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fatvr5xS.png&h=308dd739&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n讓她看自己喜歡的事物<br />\n如果對方不能分享你的喜悅<br />\n交往也沒意思<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CMCuiST.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCMCuiST.png&h=9093abbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真希望福壽同學也能嚐嚐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0x0vNMd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0x0vNMd.png&h=9ab3842d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這刻發現 我很想跟她分享一切<br />\n愛上一個人原來是這樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yHxqBEz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyHxqBEz.png&h=a5a4d4b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mjmnDSV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmjmnDSV.png&h=dc300f3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TvWrk6f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTvWrk6f.png&h=8090ec4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Pdk9ZB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Pdk9ZB.png&h=af318442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南山同學<br />\n好 那麼我們走吧<br />\n嗯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hjDEGfZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhjDEGfZ.png&h=a088a37a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A2sui2F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA2sui2F.png&h=8dd65314&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n這裡的小巷子很有趣<br />\n真好 我最喜歡這種地方<br />\n嘩你看 好漂亮呀<br />\n對吧?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mZk37WM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmZk37WM.png&h=e61d953a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n超級好吃!<br />\n對吧?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9oKDWP7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9oKDWP7.png&h=85d2f7e9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n那邊的炸雞排店好像很好吃 我們去買吧<br />\n味道...很普通<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CMSVeBO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCMSVeBO.png&h=03a33456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等等 我要再吃多一次薄餅<br />\n我無法接受以不好味的一餐作結<br />\n福壽同學 你真有趣 <br />\n什麼?哈哈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BtPgJwR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBtPgJwR.png&h=bd748df1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r8TAY5c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr8TAY5c.png&h=2920dd77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這裡不錯呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HkVPi5J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHkVPi5J.png&h=e9086636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n噢 好可愛呀<br />\n真的好可愛 是松鼠狗嗎<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8MbyLLJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8MbyLLJ.png&h=0f764068&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/px1KSqL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpx1KSqL.png&h=939779d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一隻小狗拼命追上主人 真的好可愛<br />\n南山同學 你也很有趣<br />\n什麼?<br />\n哈哈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cKy1UE1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcKy1UE1.png&h=50834f22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6pBbxrG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6pBbxrG.png&h=0db02c1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hSyYcrH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhSyYcrH.png&h=870aa3da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嗯?<br />\n沒什麼 總覺得感覺很奇妙 能和福壽同學一起<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o8JpSrJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo8JpSrJ.png&h=bf4dbc04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我也是一樣 這是我第一次的約會<br />\n南山同學是我第一次約會的對象<br />\n什麼?<br />\n大家都這樣說 但我自己從不會主動出擊<br />\n也沒人主動問我<br />\n因為福壽同學看起來很難追<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OG6bxrJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOG6bxrJ.png&h=8fca2435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以那時我很開心<br />\n一直希望有人會對我說: 我對你一見鍾情<br />\n可以告訴你一件事嗎? 我一直在留意你<br />\n什麼?<br />\n沒察覺吧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hBd1UHg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhBd1UHg.png&h=689f8f23&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ow4kqOW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fow4kqOW.png&h=1674396d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n福壽同學 <br />\n請你... 做我女朋友 好嗎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VEg3oAY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVEg3oAY.png&h=1966169b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XTxBJAZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXTxBJAZ.png&h=ddb70c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你要知道 我不是甜心呢<br />\n沒問題<br />\n<br />\n而且我很自我 有時我很自我中心<br />\n沒問題<br />\n<br />\n還有 食物會影響我的情緒<br />\n沒問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QnNRxuY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQnNRxuY.png&h=8a71ebd3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8JSFqPY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8JSFqPY.png&h=63d60da4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n這樣.. 請多多指教<br />\n我也是<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3LD9jao.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3LD9jao.png&h=3cf7bfa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對了 還有一件事<br />\n我... 很眼淺的<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PVVcgW2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPVVcgW2.png&h=5ed7f794&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"994166b9f8432895e65b445536fccd2595118037","tid":1022873,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:55:30.000Z","msg":"睇完好戲 <br />\n就要同人share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927249257550e5a297750c9b2c71982f3413ec5f","tid":1022873,"uid":18971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"994166b9f8432895e65b445536fccd2595118037","tid":1022873,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:55:30.000Z","msg":"睇完好戲 <br />\n就要同人share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T17:00:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一齊推我之前個個post <br />\n推介埋比朋友睇"},{"pid":"fea2a7e0b28e82584290b614c4b1df542c58423b","tid":1022873,"uid":18971,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T17:37:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/voAHr28.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvoAHr28.png&h=7013bd52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjNCfWu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjNCfWu.png&h=2bafc547&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南山同學!<br />\n對不起 我遲到了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r02VM3a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr02VM3a.png&h=2cfb49df&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n這是上山<br />\n幸會 我是福壽愛美<br />\n我是上山正一 <br />\n請你多多關照這小子<br />\n那算什麼意思?<br />\n我會的!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/saGC0ob.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsaGC0ob.png&h=1ffe6399&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DAK1HBw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDAK1HBw.png&h=63a4ff7c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n唏 這就是南山同學的新居<br />\n那我來幫忙!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BqJ59gx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBqJ59gx.png&h=bfae5dee&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n是個好女孩 要好好對她<br />\n對哦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UnL0Yce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUnL0Yce.png&h=da79c089&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n那我先走了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dqAsDcf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdqAsDcf.png&h=f20d651f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謝謝幫忙了<br />\n就當是入伙禮物<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rcPpFqB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrcPpFqB.png&h=4d8610a0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n上山同學 請你以後多多關照南山同學<br />\n你要小心這小子喔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rObjukf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrObjukf.png&h=171f4b02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n收聲哈哈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gaYh0sj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgaYh0sj.png&h=b9654c4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對於我們的稱呼...<br />\n我覺得叫你福壽同學好像有點正經<br />\n對 好像很見外<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9UdmHFF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9UdmHFF.png&h=4605f9ab&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n其他人會何時改變稱呼?<br />\n現在 就是現在<br />\n現在?...  那麼.. 愛美小姐<br />\n高壽先生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WnmWwy1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWnmWwy1.png&h=787a16b8&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n沒事吧? <br />\n只不過... 風沙入眼<br />\n打掃完了 我們開箱吧!<br />\n是!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0jLL9nu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0jLL9nu.png&h=ba955963&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ijPMTPa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FijPMTPa.png&h=c14fb952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只是覺得..你身材很好<br />\n變態!<br />\n不 我只是以美學角度來看 說真的!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t1V0Ygz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft1V0Ygz.png&h=bab0cc75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喔 那個 是我的救命恩人給我的<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V3ce2Je.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV3ce2Je.png&h=8ca74ccd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n她救了我的5年後 在家附近跟她巧遇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jWgO69V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjWgO69V.png&h=6f7cce44&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cJxiKWB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcJxiKWB.png&h=4d43ab76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她拜託我代為保管 直至下次見面<br />\n感覺很神秘呢...<br />\n不知道會不會再見到她呢...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LP9QA4p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLP9QA4p.png&h=d4a08fca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咦 這是你畫的嗎<br />\n對 是我小學時畫的<br />\n你真是個藝術家呢...<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bdUdyQ5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbdUdyQ5.png&h=6d572952&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n你一直都是..<br />\n嗯?<br />\n好吧 天黑之前要收拾好!<br />\n好 一起努力!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ntVL9qo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FntVL9qo.png&h=60c9c8ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wyqwkw3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwyqwkw3.png&h=44915cc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這樣沒問題嗎?<br />\n應該沒問題的<br />\n原來你要午夜前回家<br />\n對 就像灰姑娘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/scK5pYK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FscK5pYK.png&h=4997c466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n很冷...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4D1jurk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4D1jurk.png&h=992e21e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不如... 我們... 拖手吧<br />\n好.. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mKO9REF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmKO9REF.png&h=9e86ebf3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n感覺真好 跟女朋友... 這樣拖手<br />\n是我第一次 感覺真好<br />\n嗯...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/37T2sc1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F37T2sc1.png&h=fb127569&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n口甜舌滑!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4wfNd9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4wfNd9.png&h=da4bafa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n妳真的很眼淺呢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xiiqp0P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXiiqp0P.png&h=b21ed4fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明天見<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdrLp0P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdrLp0P.png&h=8fa88433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明天見 成為了我們之間的密碼"},{"pid":"a93de891bf0b8f445a7eac7bae1c73ffa2f4931f","tid":1022873,"uid":68395,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T19:59:35.000Z","msg":"睇左樓主之前個post, 所以去睇套戲, 岩岩睇完, 真係好虐心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">女主(20歲)最後一日就係男主(20歲)第一日見到女主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"803e3442b53efb28b3ae571241fda7ab277d8fa2","tid":1022873,"uid":18971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a93de891bf0b8f445a7eac7bae1c73ffa2f4931f","tid":1022873,"uid":68395,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T19:59:35.000Z","msg":"睇左樓主之前個post, 所以去睇套戲, 岩岩睇完, 真係好虐心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">女主(20歲)最後一日就係男主(20歲)第一日見到女主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T05:14:02.000Z","msg":"請重刷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"838d4ee6b6189b190e91f6f9d21778b9e74b0386","tid":1022873,"uid":18971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T18:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xqTFT1K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxqTFT1K.png&h=6ab52a73&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2vFH7mL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2vFH7mL.png&h=926e5d2c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n之後我們幾乎每天都會約會<br />\n我來拿<br />\n謝謝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QpktitU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQpktitU.png&h=a293431f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n不要掉下去哦<br />\n什麼? 我才不是那麼論盡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZvTFT2u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZvTFT2u.png&h=9206edd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n晚餐是什麼?<br />\n秘密 你猜猜<br />\n唔...咖哩?<br />\nBU BU<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GuB8iuK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGuB8iuK.png&h=064cdacd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jz0hbPL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJz0hbPL.png&h=1c4a88ee&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FUDnnWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFUDnnWr.png&h=83523bc3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n可以影張相嗎?<br />\n什麼?好吧<br />\n看這邊.. 笑一個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ALZRggT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FALZRggT.png&h=ff695ac1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n你去那邊喝茶等等 沒有熱水壺 <br />\n就用這個煲水吧 杯在那邊<br />\n遵命<br />\n給你<br />\n好的!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etdbghN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetdbghN.png&h=916bdf74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完成!<br />\n嘩 好像很美味!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gSL1Dv8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgSL1Dv8.png&h=eb3ef970&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我不客氣了<br />\n請慢用<br />\n嘩! 好好味! 超級好味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yq4Ny5h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyq4Ny5h.png&h=f59dfa91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這個炆牛肉跟我媽媽煮的一模一樣<br />\n一定是因為加了秘密材料朱古力<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NJ6gsqi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNJ6gsqi.png&h=922aabf8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n等等...你怎知道的?<br />\n知道什麼?<br />\n妳怎知我媽的炆牛肉都加朱古力<br />\n你之前說過<br />\n好像沒說過<br />\n是嗎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZYq5c8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZYq5c8.png&h=2cc66941&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n講開又講 之前也發生過類似的事<br />\n什麼?<br />\n我畫長頸鹿那次 你說它會貼堂 結果之後真的貼堂了<br />\n碰巧而已<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vSUYFNz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvSUYFNz.png&h=9181f31d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/va7fH0V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fva7fH0V.png&h=012eb9d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n妳是不是...  有預知未來的特異功能?<br />\n如果我有的話又如何?<br />\n什麼?<br />\n如果的真的有預知未來的特異功能... 你會怎樣做?<br />\n我會覺得很厲害<br />\n那當然啦! 如果能預知未來 我賭博一定會嬴<br />\n我一定會努力賺錢<br />\n真是個男子漢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9pDFT8r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9pDFT8r.png&h=51acf680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果我說我知道你的未來 你會怎辦?<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A0UUYz6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA0UUYz6.png&h=3df3a527&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n不...不用了 我不想知道<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SdD6PGN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSdD6PGN.png&h=7149d7c1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n很可惜我不知道 畢竟的只是個普通人<br />\n好了 快吃吧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/veAAH3j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FveAAH3j.png&h=4ea817f8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HpwTuJm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHpwTuJm.png&h=68b09d77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喂<br />\n喂<br />\n好久沒見了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pd7vwWF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPd7vwWF.png&h=5a10f99c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一切順利嗎?<br />\n她為我親手下廚<br />\n好 好 那真好<br />\n哈哈"},{"pid":"36237a58568d5d31cc1afd229c2a62cb311414e3","tid":1022873,"uid":184778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:44:37.000Z","msg":"Youtube見過個fan made mv<br />\n用女主角度出發 <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">由最後一日開始去到第一日</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f904a87945a0b4357c2b756d897d7fe8159feced","tid":1022873,"uid":18971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36237a58568d5d31cc1afd229c2a62cb311414e3","tid":1022873,"uid":184778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:44:37.000Z","msg":"Youtube見過個fan made mv<br />\n用女主角度出發 <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">由最後一日開始去到第一日</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\